---
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>CDS Cold Storage — Refrigeration, Packaging & Shipping</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #1a1a2e; }

    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; background: rgba(10,25,47,0.95);
      padding: 1rem 2rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center; z-index: 100;
    }
    .logo-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .logo-wrap img { height: 40px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; }
    .logo-wrap span { color: #00d4ff; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; }
    nav a { color: #ccd6f6; text-decoration: none; margin-left: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav a:hover { color: #00d4ff; }

    /* HERO WITH VIDEO */
    .hero {
      position: relative; min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      text-align: center; padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-video {
      position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      min-width: 100%; min-height: 100%;
      width: auto; height: auto;
      object-fit: cover; z-index: 0;
    }
    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: rgba(10, 25, 47, 0.7); z-index: 1;
    }
    .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
    .hero h1 { color: #e6f1ff; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #00d4ff; }
    .hero p { color: #ccd6f6; font-size: 1.2rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-btn {
      background: #00d4ff; color: #0a192f; padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
      border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-btn:hover { background: #64ffda; }

    .services-bg { background: #f8faff; padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    section { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    h2 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #0a192f; }
    .line { width: 60px; height: 4px; background: #00d4ff; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }

    .services-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .card .icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .card h3 { color: #0a192f; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .card p { color: #5a6a80; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }

    .about-bg { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    .about-inner {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center;
    }
    .about-inner img { width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; object-fit: cover; height: 350px; }
    .about-text p { color: #5a6a80; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    .gallery-section { background: #f8faff; padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem;
    }
    .gallery-grid img {
      width: 100%; height: 220px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; transition: transform 0.3s;
    }
    .gallery-grid img:hover { transform: scale(1.03); }

    .contact-bg { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
    form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
    input, textarea, select {
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #d0d7e3; border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem; font-family: inherit; background: white;
    }
    input:focus, textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: #00d4ff; }
    textarea { min-height: 140px; resize: vertical; }
    button[type="submit"] {
      background: #0a192f; color: white; border: none; padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer;
    }
    button[type="submit"]:hover { background: #112240; }

    footer {
      background: #0a192f; color: #8892b0; text-align: center; padding: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    footer span { color: #00d4ff; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <div class="logo-wrap">
      <img src="/cdslogo.png" alt="CDS Cold Storage Logo" />
      <span>CDS Cold Storage</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#services">Services</a>
      <a href="#gallery">Gallery</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO WITH VIDEO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <video class="hero-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline>
      <source src="/hero-video.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Cold Storage <span>Done Right</span></h1>
      <p>Professional refrigeration, packaging, and shipping solutions — keeping your products fresh from our facility to your door.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="hero-btn">Get a Free Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <div id="about" class="about-bg">
    <section>
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <div class="line"></div>
      <div class="about-inner">
        <img src="/facility1.JPG" alt="CDS Cold Storage facility" />
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>CDS Cold Storage is a trusted partner for businesses that depend on reliable cold chain solutions. We specialize in keeping perishable products safe, fresh, and ready for delivery.</p>
          <p>With state-of-the-art refrigeration technology and a dedicated team, we handle your products with the care and precision they deserve — from storage to final shipment.</p>
          <p>Whether you're a small producer or a large distributor, we have the capacity and expertise to meet your needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <div id="services" class="services-bg">
    <section>
      <h2>Our Services</h2>
      <div class="line"></div>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">🧊</div>
          <h3>Cold Storage Refrigeration</h3>
          <p>State-of-the-art refrigerated storage maintaining precise temperatures to preserve the quality and safety of your products.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">📦</div>
          <h3>Packaging</h3>
          <p>Specialized cold-chain packaging designed to protect perishables during transit — from insulated liners to dry ice solutions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon">🚚</div>
          <h3>Shipping</h3>
          <p>Reliable temperature-controlled shipping coordination ensuring your goods arrive on time and in perfect condition.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- GALLERY -->
  <div id="gallery" class="gallery-section">
    <section>
      <h2>Our Facility</h2>
      <div class="line"></div>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <img src="/facility1.JPG" alt="CDS Cold Storage facility" />
        <img src="/facility2.JPG" alt="CDS Cold Storage facility" />
        <img src="/facility3.JPG" alt="CDS Cold Storage facility" />
        <img src="/facility4.JPG" alt="CDS Cold Storage facility" />
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <div id="contact" class="contact-bg">
    <section>
      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      <div class="line"></div>
      <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xojpjvkb" method="POST">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required />
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" required />
        <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone Number" />
        <select name="service">
          <option value="">— Service Interested In —</option>
          <option>Cold Storage Refrigeration</option>
          <option>Packaging</option>
          <option>Shipping</option>
          <option>All Services</option>
        </select>
        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Tell us about your needs..."></textarea>
        <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 <span>CDS Cold Storage</span> · All rights reserved</p>
    <p style="margin-top:0.5rem;">📞 YOUR PHONE &nbsp;·&nbsp; ✉️ YOUR EMAIL</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
